{0 day11-solution}

Pure dependency graph types and operations. {!Day11_solution.Deps.t} is the
fundamental type — a map from packages to their direct dependencies —
used throughout the system. {!Day11_solution.Solve_result} carries both the build
dependency graph (acyclic) and the doc dependency graph (may have
cycles) returned by the solver. {!Day11_solution.Json} handles serialization
for caching and inter-process communication. {!Day11_solution.Universe} computes a
hash of a package's transitive dependency set, used to distinguish
build contexts. {!Day11_solution.Rdeps} provides reverse dependency lookup.

No I/O, no solver, no opam-format dependency beyond types. This
library sits at the bottom of the dependency hierarchy.

